            <title>[KAFKA-9644] incrementalAlterConfigs OpType.APPEND on unset property fails with NullPointerException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-9644</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Running incrementalAlterConfigs with an OpType.APPEND when the config property doesn&apos;t already exist fails with a NullPointerException on the broker.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Attached is a patch to the PlaintextAdminIntegrationTest demonstrating this failure and the test output showing the NPE.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
